パッケージ jp.co.rakuten.util.multiindex

Container can multi-indexing with flexibly like 'C++ BOOST multi-index'.

参照先:
          説明

インタフェースの概要
Index<T> Index base I/F of MultiIndex
 

クラスの概要
IdentityIndex<T extends Comparable<T>> The index is sorted in order of data-type identity (Depends on Comparable).
IndexBy<T> Indexes definition.
MultiIndex<T> Multi indexable container.
NonUniqueIndex<K extends Comparable<K>,T> Base class of non-unique index.
OrderedNonUniqueIndex<K extends Comparable<K>,T> The index is sorted in order of specified field.
OrderedUniqueIndex<K extends Comparable<K>,T> The index is sorted in order of specified field.
Record<T> MultiIndex's record.
SequenceIndex<T> The index is sorted in order of insertion.
UniqueIndex<K extends Comparable<K>,T> Base class of unique index.

Container can multi-indexing with flexibly like 'C++ BOOST multi-index'.
